Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.36,1:22:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't got any problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.86,1:22:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was not happy to suddenly come into conscious awareness of physical existence again.
